Knight of Coins						KEY:Paladin Archetype ~ Knight of Coins												CATEGORY:Archetype			TYPE:Archetype.PaladinArchetype																		PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Paladin Archetype ~ Knight of Coins],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Paladin_Archetype_ClassSkills=True,Paladin_Archetype_DetectEvil=True,Paladin_Archetype_Mercy3=True,Paladin_Archetype_Mercy9=True,Paladin_Archetype_Mercy15=True]																																			DESC:Servants of gods who revere wealth, knights of coins promote fair trade and stable commerce between cities and between nations. Many of these knights are Abadarans, and some have also taken the sacred shield archetype. Regardless, knights of coins know that a prosperous city can uplift and enrich more people than pious prayers alone.																																																																																														ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Knight of Coins ~ Class Skills|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Knight of Coins ~ Eye for Forgeries|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Knight of Coins ~ Blessing of Prosperity|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=3																																																																																																																																									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.28																FACT:Paladin_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_DetectEvil|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_Mercy3|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_Mercy9|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_Mercy15|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_DetectEvil|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_Mercy3|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_Mercy9|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_Mercy15|true

